(1339, 195, 'testimonial_section_text', '“Growing in our spiritual path isn’t about turning a blind eye and bypassing the suffering within and around us. It’s about understanding that we are a part of all we experience. Empowered we unite, we grow. We commit to continue to follow our hearts. We put down our illusions of division and realize how much we have to learn from LOVE, the true teacher, within us all.”\r\n-Mama Medicine'),
