(2348, 220, 'about_content_0_about_content_p', 'My birth chart tells me I am a Scorpio sun, Cancer Moon and Leo Rising.'),
(2349, 220, '_about_content_0_about_content_p', 'field_668cda59529dd'),
(2350, 220, 'about_content_1_about_content_p', 'I am American-born, and a DNA test tells me I descend from mostly Irish, then a travelers blend of (in order of percentage) Sicilian, Italian, Spanish, Portuguese, French, Scandinavian, North African and West Asian, the rest of what shows up is in negligible traces.'),
(2351, 220, '_about_content_1_about_content_p', 'field_668cda59529dd'),
(2352, 220, 'about_content_2_about_content_p', 'I was raised in New England as a cult level strict evangelical northern baptist, this is very purposeful because it is where I was first introduced to Ritual Baths and where I heard Jesus’s message of the power of love which deeply resonated with me. The rest of the religion made no sense to me, the people were so wound up, tucked in and depressed, women were shamed, even as a child could clearly see that my church was misinterpreting Jesus’s message. When I was twelve and my family fell apart, I  moved away from that religion and reached more toward my spirituality in a mystical and undefined way.'),
(2353, 220, '_about_content_2_about_content_p', 'field_668cda59529dd'),
(2354, 220, 'about_content_3_about_content_p', 'Because there was no university for what I wanted to study I had to find my own way.'),
